# Criacao de um POD
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: frontend
  labels:
    app: recargacel
spec:
  containers:
  - name: nginx
    image: nginx:1.14.2
    ports:
    - containerPort: 80


# Criacao de um ReplicaSet
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: ReplicaSet
metadata:
  name: frontend
  labels:
    app: recargacel
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: recargacel
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: recargacel
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: nginx
        image: nginx:1.14.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80


Aplicar um POD
Aplicar o RS
Modificar a versao do RS para 1.16
Aplicar o RS



